{
  "stem": "9102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was trying to move back to turn around to see one more look at them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She says, don't look back because there are all kind of collaborators living around there, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so that's how I moved, went with the underground to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then in the train, of course, we had inspection all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I really don't know how they managed to get that done, but they managed to get me down to the southern province.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't have false papers as such.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you know, it's just-- I don't know what they really had to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe the underground did have some papers, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never had.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, nothing then.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was just going on holidays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was taking me to, you know, to the southern part to go on holidays for a couple-- because in Amsterdam there was, you know, limited food supplies and dangers and all this.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, you know, I was told I was to go, go on holidays.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I ended up in Limburg, in the city of Heerlen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was brought to a family [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what had offered to hide Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, I got there, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, you miss your parents and all this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the part was, the next day I was outside on the road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And hold and below, there I see my brother who had gone a couple weeks before me and I didn't know where he was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He just happened to be with people right across the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was, you know, that didn't go, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since my brother had been already at those people for a couple weeks, they decided right away I had to move again.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
